sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Command as "Procurement Command"
    participant Context as "arckit-context Hook"
    participant Requirements as "ARC-{PID}-REQ-v*.md"
    participant Research as "vendors/*.md<br/>tech-notes/*.md"
    participant Template as "Template System"
    participant Output as "Procurement Artifact"
    
    User->>Command: /arckit.sow or /arckit.gcloud-search<br/>or /arckit.dos or /arckit.evaluate
    
    Command->>Context: Request project context
    Context->>Requirements: Scan for requirements artifact
    Context->>Research: Scan vendors/ and tech-notes/
    Context-->>Command: Inject: requirements list<br/>research artifacts list
    
    Command->>Requirements: Read BR/FR/NFR/INT/DR requirements
    Command->>Research: Read vendor profiles (if exist)
    
    alt G-Cloud Search
        Command->>Command: Extract technical criteria from NFRs
        Command->>Command: WebSearch: Digital Marketplace API
        Command-->>Command: Parse: supplier, service, price, features
    end
    
    alt DOS Pack
        Command->>Command: Extract essential vs desirable skills
        Command->>Command: Technology-agnostic success criteria
    end
    
    Command->>Template: Resolve template<br/>(custom or default)
    Template-->>Command: sow-template.md or<br/>gcloud-template.md or<br/>dos-template.md
    
    Command->>Output: Generate artifact with<br/>Document Control table
    Output->>Output: Traceability: REQ-xxx â Section
    
    Command-->>User: Summary: artifact location<br/>shortlisted vendors (if search)
